{"title":"Farewell’s New Basket Bag","link":"https://theradavist.com/farewell-basket-bag/","date":1737731818000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_01.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_01.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Santa Fe, New Mexico-based <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/farewell/\" target=\"_blank\">Farewell</a> is releasing its newest bag today at 12 Noon MST. The bag is dubbed the “Despite all my sage, I am still just a bag in a cage” and, as you guessed it, is a basket bag. </em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_03.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_03.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_02.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_02.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_04.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Farewell_Basket_Bag_04.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>This large tote has a zipper closure and two side hooks that roll over and attach to your Wald 139 basket. It’s made from XPAC, comes in a variety of colors, and is a whopping 27 liters in size.</p>\n<p>Keep an eye on <a href=\"https://www.thisisfarewell.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Farewell’s webshop</a> at 12 Noon MST.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/farewell-basket-bag/\">Farewell’s New Basket Bag</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"d4c0ca7e46b107082d9ef2ee3e201d14c389f4c4df744a627936e5c337dbb636","category":"Cycling"}